{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-5","storyName":"多萝西的承诺","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"原来进入实验室才是拓荒者们的真正目的，他们认为多萝西是神秘生物失控的始作俑者，而在他们发动攻击之时，这种神秘的生物却仿佛具备了自我意识，主动保护多萝西。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["塞雷娅","缪尔赛思","Mechanist","斐尔迪南","霍尔海雅","埃琳娜","桑尼","赫默","多萝西","拓荒队成员","格雷伊","玛丽","形状奇特的物体"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"dialog","id":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g8_alley_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"dialog","id":8},{"type":"character","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":11},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......缪尔赛思。","id":13,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",0]},{"type":"character","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"唔......嗯......","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#7$1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我没有料到你在这里。","id":17,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"抱歉。","id":18,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",6]},{"type":"character","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"抱......歉？","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#7$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"要不是博士提醒，我差一点亲手杀死你。","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"这就是敌人想看见的吗？他们想让你变成杀害前同僚的凶手？","id":24,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"未必。","id":26,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我能及时收手，除了博士出声提醒，还有她那句话的缘故。","id":27,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"“不要急着与任何人为敌”——她有意预告了缪尔赛思的出现。","id":28,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"character","id":30},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"32","text":"这解释了她之前的行为疑点。"},{"id":"32","text":"她想引导我们找到缪尔赛思。"}],"values":[],"id":31},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":32,"end":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"难不成她故意把缪尔赛思送了回来？","id":34,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"可刚才的情况明明很凶险，谁能保证缪尔赛思不会死在我们手上......","id":36,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我知道了，她不在乎缪尔赛思到底是死是活。","id":38,"figure":["avg_npc_521_1",0],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":39},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"41","text":"这对她来说是一场测试。"},{"id":"46","text":"她想让塞雷娅加快行动。"}],"values":[],"id":40},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":41,"end":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......测试动力甲的技术，也测试我和罗德岛的反应。","id":43,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#3$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"她在酒吧里说的每一句话都是对我的试探。","id":45,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",2]},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":46,"end":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"她仍在引导我们走向对她有利的方向。","id":48,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",8],"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":49},{"type":"character","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"呃呃呃......！","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#5$1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"缪尔赛思，你好些了吗？","id":53,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#6$1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"他们在好几个小时前给你注射了镇定剂，你在动力甲里面的时候已经基本恢复了清醒。","id":55,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"你当前体验到的眩晕与麻痹，主要是缺氧和精神恐惧带来的后遗症。","id":56,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我已经为你做了一些应急处理，但完全恢复还需要半个小时左右。","id":57,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"character","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"阻......阻......","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#6$1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"阻止？","id":61,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#6$1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"阻止......谁？","id":63,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"你是想让我们阻止那个把你关进动力甲里的人吗？","id":64,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"是那位黎博利吗？","id":65,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",5]},{"type":"character","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"不......","id":67},{"type":"text","text":"因为着急，缪尔赛思的额头和手背上冒出了细密的汗珠。","id":68},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":69},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"40","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"她突然抓住了你的手，伴随着她的动作，水滴纷纷浮了起来，狠狠撞上你的衣襟。","id":71},{"type":"text","text":"水在深色的布料上迅速洇开，组成了一行讯息。","id":72},{"type":"text","text":"不是那个黎博利的名字，不是斐尔迪南，而是......","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......359。","id":75,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"359号基地。","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_532_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":79},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":81},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g9_headquarter.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":84,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你很少来这里。","id":88,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","id":89},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","fadetime":"1","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"好歹你送了我一张临时工牌。","id":93,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#8$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"“文献学顾问”——莱茵这种科技公司，真的需要这方面的顾问吗？","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"你的心情很好，这是否说明，实验进展还不错？","id":97,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"别提实验。","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"十分钟。像我这样的人，一天下来，只有十分钟是我自己的。","id":101,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我可以把这时间花在跟孩子们打视频电话上，也可以用这短暂的时间和埃琳娜他们一起吃个晚饭。","id":103,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"但我更喜欢什么都不做，就站在这里看看这一切。","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"外面只有街道。","id":107,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"是啊，这就是一切。","id":109,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":110},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":112},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_29_g7_mainstreet_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","id":115},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_523_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":117},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-400","fadetime":"10","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.3","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":120},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":121},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","id":123},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_524_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":126},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"400","fadetime":"10","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.3","id":128},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":129},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":131},{"type":"character","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"像这样工作一整天，他们必定满身疲惫。为什么他们的脸上看不见沮丧，脚步也依然轻快？","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"因为“机会”。","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"他们相信自己的辛劳将有机会带给全家人更好的生活。","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......就跟城外那些拓荒者一样。","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"当然，就像拓荒者。","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"特里蒙，三驮镇。","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"曾经只有三匹驮兽带着七个拓荒者，在这片土地上建起了第一个简陋的定居点。","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"如今呢？看看我们脚下的街道。","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"这里聚集了最有活力的开拓者和开拓者们的后代。没有哪个国家富有哥伦比亚的进取精神。","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"哥伦比亚的繁荣给了人们信心，而人们日复一日地不断前进也会给哥伦比亚带来生机。","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"只要哥伦比亚保持飞速前进，那这片土地上每一个人的生活也都在前进。","id":143},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":146},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g9_headquarter.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":147},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我知道你们是怎么看我的。你，克丽斯腾，塞雷娅......你们都叫我“投机者”。","id":150,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"能抓住机会的，可都是聪明人。","id":152,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"谢谢。","id":154,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我不否认，我喜欢站在这里，这个更高的位置，而不是下面。","id":156,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"但我配得上我得到的机会。","id":158,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我的项目带来财富，财富推动下一个项目，技术因此而不断进步——","id":160,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我们将站在其他所有国家前面，引领整个泰拉进入新的时代。","id":162,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"到那个时候，后人会竖起不朽的丰碑，上面将刻有我们的名字。","id":164,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我们？","id":166,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"胜利属于每一个开拓者。","id":168,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"——","id":170,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"十分钟快到了。","id":172,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#1$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"你可没给我说话的时间。","id":174,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"霍尔海雅，我知道你来找我是要说什么。","id":176,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"嗯？","id":178,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我原谅你。","id":180,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......","id":182,"figure":["avg_npc_536_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"克丽斯腾，缪尔赛思，塞雷娅，帕尔维斯......还有你。我没有时间浪费在猜测你们各自的小心思上。","id":184,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"多萝西的实验距离成功只有一步之遥——","id":186,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我只想要那个最后的结果。","id":188,"figure":["avg_npc_522_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":190},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":191},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":192},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/86/Avg_bg_29_g5_laboratory.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":193},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":195,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"桑、桑尼......","id":197,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",11]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"多萝西说过了，这里没有危险......你们为什么都掏出了弓弩？","id":198,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"没有危险？","id":200,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"乌比卡博士，你错了。","id":202,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"在我们面前的就是最大的危险。","id":204,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你是指......多萝西？","id":206,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我还以为你愿意听我们解释......","id":208,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......抱歉。","id":210,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"麻烦你和两位医生让一让。我们的目标从来都不是你们。","id":212,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"可是......","id":214,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","name2":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"埃琳娜，我们上了这位领队先生的当。","id":216,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"刚才那场被阻止的针对乔伊丝的袭击，只是一场刻意的表演。","id":217,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"他先后让我们看到了他的愤怒、他的犹豫和他的底线，只为了掩盖一件事——","id":218,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"从始至终，他都做好了真正去犯罪的准备。","id":219,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我没有料到迈尔会动手。为了取得你们......尤其是乌比卡博士的信任，我原本安排了萨姆来扮演更过激的一方。","id":223,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"算了，这些都不重要。","id":225,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我们已经如愿来到了这里，找到了问题的源头——","id":227,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......我？","id":229,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"桑尼，你策划那场绑架，又一路来到这里，是想杀了我吗？","id":231,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我能不能问一问......为什么？","id":233,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"text","text":"依旧是温柔到能渗进最坚硬的心脏里的声音。","id":234},{"type":"text","text":"还有那双湿润的、微微睁大的眼睛。","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"那么无辜，那么惊讶，甚至带着一丝受伤。","id":236},{"type":"text","text":"就好像该被指责的是被迫拿起武器自卫的他们一样。","id":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"为什么......你问我为什么？","id":239,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"因为我都看见了。","id":241,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你造出来的怪物一路追杀我们，你用我的同伴们的鲜血喂养这些怪物......","id":243,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你这个......邪恶的......","id":245,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"并不存在什么怪物！","id":247,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"那些只是实验的副产物，由一种对神经信号敏感的特殊物质构成......","id":249,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#3$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......不，埃琳娜，这不是桑尼的臆测。","id":251,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#4$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"他的意思恐怕是，他的确早就见过那些银色物体......","id":253,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#4$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"甚至更多。","id":255,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......是的。","id":257,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"三天前，我偷偷溜进了实验区......我想来找你。","id":259,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我想......呃，那时候我想来问问你，我能不能报名成为受试者。","id":261,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"领队，你不是说，成为受试者有很大风险，这些大公司很可能在骗我们吗？","id":263,"figure":["avg_npc_534_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"风险......哈......哈哈哈！","id":265,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#9$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"对不起。萨姆，我是个言行不一致的混蛋......","id":267,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#9$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"可我想纠正我曾经的错误。","id":269,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"听着，各位——","id":271,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"那一夜，我看到银色的怪物在她身边凝聚成形，她对它们说话，就好像那是她的宠物一样。","id":273,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"多萝西·弗兰克斯就是这场灾难的始作俑者。","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":278},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/64/Avg_bg_29_g3_cottage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":279},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","fadetime":"1","id":281},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"玛丽女士，我说的这些，您是不是很难接受？","id":283,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......我不是喜欢看科幻电影的那类人。","id":285,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"那或许您可以看一眼这封信。","id":287,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"信？","id":289,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"桑尼先生跟我巡完线之后，可能料到了之后会有危险，把这封信交给了我。","id":291,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"他说——“万一我出事了，请把这封信交给玛丽·班纳”。","id":292,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"他应该不介意......您提前看到信的内容吧？","id":293,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......给我吧。","id":295,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"............","id":296,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#8$2","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"女士，信上......说了什么？","id":298,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",17]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#5$1","id":299},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那家伙到底去了哪里？！","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"呃......","id":303,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",14]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"格雷伊，你并不了解桑尼·罗马诺。","id":305,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"他的内心充满了愤恨。因为那份该死的保险......","id":307,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"又是保险......","id":309,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",14]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"对，在哥伦比亚，这是个刻在所有感染者脑子里的词语。","id":311,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"也许......很多外头的人会觉得哥伦比亚对感染者已经足够仁慈。","id":312,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"“只要能支付医疗保险费用，就可以获得后续正常生活的保障”——听起来是不是还挺公正的？","id":313,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"桑尼在刚得病的时候也是这么对我说的。","id":314,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"可是结果呢？","id":315,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"那是不是一笔......非常巨额的费用？","id":317,"figure":["avg_1027_greyy2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"我只知道就算我当一辈子警察，不吃不喝都负担不起。","id":319,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那玩意儿就不是用来保障感染者生活的......巨额保费与他们能得到的药品完全不匹配。","id":320,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那就是一笔罚款，一条隐藏的规则，用来变相逼迫感染者走上被设定好的道路。","id":321,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"桑尼......罗马诺那家伙从来不肯正视现实。","id":322,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#5$1","name2":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"不阻止他的话，他真的有可能犯下不可饶恕的罪行。","id":324,"figure":["avg_npc_527_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":326},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":327},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/86/Avg_bg_29_g5_laboratory.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":328},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"桑尼，你看到的并不是怪物，也不是我的宠物。","id":331,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"但他们的确与我的实验有关。","id":333,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......你承认了。","id":335,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"真相对你们而言并无益处。","id":337,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"知道得越多，你们就越危险。","id":339,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......替别人做决定，是不是你们这些上层人士最爱做的事？","id":341,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"先放下这些利器好不好？仪器都很脆弱。","id":343,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"或者请瞄准这里。","id":345,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我......我不介意的。","id":347,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"character","id":349},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.8","id":350},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":351},{"type":"text","text":"她朝拓荒者们走了一步，弓弩几乎碰到了她的身体。","id":352},{"type":"text","text":"桑尼的手微微颤抖了一下，他强迫自己将视线从那双温和的眼睛上移开。","id":353},{"type":"text","text":"这也是邪恶的伎俩，是迫使他们再次屈服的法术。","id":354},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你不怕死？","id":356,"figure":["avg_npc_535_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我怕。","id":358,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"可我更怕你们伤害自己。","id":360,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"桑尼，你不是凶手，你的同伴们也不是。你们只是一群想过上更好生活的普通人。","id":361,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"你不是也想过参加我的实验吗？","id":363,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"还有机会的。只要加入我们，你就能得到你最渴望的东西。","id":364,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我永远不会对你们说不。","id":365,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":366},{"type":"character","id":367},{"type":"text","text":"她向拓荒者们伸出了一只手，仿佛正在等待他们握上去。","id":368},{"type":"text","text":"她难道不明白，他们是来杀她的吗？","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"不能看她。她的眼睛，她的手，全都不能看。太柔软了。","id":370},{"type":"text","text":"自从不得不走上荒野，城市和城市里的人都在冷硬地说着拒绝。","id":371},{"type":"text","text":"她正在控制他们。她就是这样控制住了那些可悲的意志软弱的同伴。","id":372},{"type":"text","text":"可是“机会”......","id":373},{"type":"text","text":"这个词语，我们有多久没听见了？","id":374},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue