银色造物！","id":401,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"它们是怎么跟过来的？我没有看见......","id":403,"figure":["avg_135_halo_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#4$1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......桑尼是对的。","id":405,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#4$1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这间实验室就是它们的诞生地......而且，你不觉得奇怪吗？","id":407,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#4$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"它们......好像在保护多萝西。","id":409,"figure":["avg_108_silent_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"停下来，不要伤害彼此......","id":411,"figure":["avg_4048_doroth_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_533_1#1$1","id":412},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_liquidmetal","volume":"1","id":413},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"形状奇特的物体","text":"——！","id":415,"figure":["avg_npc_533_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"它来了！","id":417,"figure":["avg_npc_534_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_hammer","volume":"0.8","id":421},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.3","id":422},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"character","id":425},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_533_1#1$1","id":426},{"type":"c